channel.title: [PI] Invisible Items
channel.description:
I have a problem with some items being invisible, they are just completely random items such as crushed gems and goblin mail. I've looked it up but no one has a fix, they just say to replace the model (I have nothing to replace them with). I'm sure there's quite a few invisible items and I actually need some of them.
How do I fix them? If I need new models can you please give them to me, it would be much appreciated. At this point a new client is not acceptable because I've already put months into this one.

item.title: [PI] Invisible Items
item.dc:creator: @Christmas_tree Christmas_tree
item.description:
@Christmas_tree wrote:

drubrkletern:

Could be a messed up cache you could try a different one

I’d have gone with the cache as well, otherwise it may be your client attempting to override some ID’s with custom items.
